requirement.en: You have 3 or more LIGHT Attribute Machine Type monsters in your Graveyard.

effect.en: Change 1 face-up Level 4 or lower monster on your opponent's field to face-down Defense Position. Then, you can Special Summon 1 Level 5 Machine Type monster from your hand face-up to your field.
